item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: gt3dev
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

[frame style='alignnone' title='' width='870' height='' url='http://www.gt3themes.com/wordpress-themes/dixit/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/adm-contacts.jpg'][/frame]";s:14:"padding_bottom";s:21:"module_medium_padding";}i:112;a:9:{s:4:"size";s:9:"block_1_1";s:4:"name";s:9:"text_area";s:7:"caption";s:9:"Text area";s:3:"key";s:3:"112";s:12:"heading_text";s:12:"View Options";s:12:"heading_size";s:2:"h4";s:13:"heading_color";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:966:"

View Options tab arms you with the vest scope of options on how you can change the color theme of your website. You can not only change the main color theme of your website but also change the page layout. You have three options for this purpose.

Clean layout allows you to set clean plane layout that will suit perfectly for the business or corporate websites. Color and pattern image will be applied for the footer section only.

Boxed layout allows you to change page layout and place background color behind the page with the pattern image, that will go above the background color but behind the page.

Full background image should be used in case you want to set background image and set color for the footer section along with the pattern image if needed.

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: gt3dev
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
